Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.13,0:01:17.51,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Day and night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.01,0:01:20.68,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}We searched along the rails
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.68,0:01:23.77,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Hoping to find another trail
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.97,0:01:25.48,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Leading to heaven
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.48,0:01:28.06,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}The heavens are waiting for motion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.06,0:01:30.77,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Fired up for action
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.77,0:01:31.90,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}There's no gain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.90,0:01:32.65,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Only pain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.65,0:01:33.48,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Only pain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.48,0:01:34.19,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Only pain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.19,0:01:34.94,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Only pain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.94,0:01:35.78,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}All this pain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:37.95,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}My pains don't exist to entertain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.95,0:01:40.37,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Count with me, one two three
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.37,0:01:43.79,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}How many liters can you bleed?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.20,0:01:47.58,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}How many turns you plan to last?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.58,0:01:50.13,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}How many lives you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.58,0:01:52.42,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I saw a star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.42,0:01:55.63,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Brightening up the dark
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:02:04.47,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}So don't you stop my fires from burning our everything
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.47,0:02:09.35,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}You and me are nothing but temporary
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.35,0:02:14.65,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Don't you start begging for mercy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.65,0:02:16.15,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}For when I win
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:17.90,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I won't forgive
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:19.45,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}And I shall win
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.45,0:02:20.99,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}And I shall win
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.99,0:02:27.75,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Yes, I shall win your one-sided game
